# Cursor Rules (Root Adapter)

Project AI harness lives in `/ai`.

## Must-do
- Start at `ai/MEMORY.md`.
- Follow the selected workflow prompt in `ai/prompts/`.
- Keep edits small and reversible.
- Verify before finalizing.
- Update harness docs after meaningful work.

## Must-not
- No broad refactors without explicit user request.
- No technology assumptions not present in repo/docs.
- No "done" claims without verification evidence.

## Completion checklist
- [ ] Changes implemented
- [ ] Verification executed
- [ ] `ai/logs/SESSION_LOG.md` updated
- [ ] `ai/logs/CHANGELOG_AI.md` updated if needed
- [ ] Relevant `/ai` knowledge files updated
